  - Corrective: updated get_deal_health_color to snake_case stages
  - Corrective: updated update_deal_v1 terminal check to closed/dead
  - Corrective: replaced DEAL_IMMUTABLE with CONFLICT (valid envelope code)
  - Updated existing test files 10_8_4, 10_8_5, 10_8_6

20260419000005_10_11A_rpcs.sql
  - 14 RPCs implemented:
    get_acq_kpis_v1
    list_acq_deals_v1 (filter: all/new/analyzing/offer_sent/under_contract/follow_ups)
    get_acq_deal_v1
    update_seller_info_v1
