    return_to_acq_v1
    return_to_dispo_v1
    list_deal_media_v1
    register_deal_media_v1 (catches unique_violation, returns CONFLICT)
    delete_deal_media_v1 (returns storage_path for server-side deletion)
  - All SECURITY DEFINER, fixed search_path, REVOKE ALL + GRANT authenticated
  - All derive tenant from current_tenant_id()
  - check_workspace_write_allowed_v1() on all mutators

=== Stage Values (canonical, locked) ===
new, analyzing, offer_sent, under_contract, dispo, tc, closed, dead

=== Stage Transitions (server-enforced) ===
new → analyzing (start_analysis)
analyzing → offer_sent (send_offer)
offer_sent → under_contract (mark_contract_signed)
under_contract → dispo (handoff_to_dispo_v1 only)
dispo → tc (handoff_to_tc_v1 only)
dispo → under_contract (return_to_acq_v1)
tc → dispo (return_to_dispo_v1)
any active → dead (mark_deal_dead_v1, dead_reason required)

